<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hasten" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hasten,</orth> 1) intr. to make haste, to move with swiftness: <bibl n="shak. son 60.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 60, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.189" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 1, 189</bibl>.<lb />2) tr. to push on, to urge on, to put to speed: <bibl n="shak. aww 2.3.223" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 3, 223</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.3.156" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 3, 156</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.363" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 363</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.2.16" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.4.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 4, 1</bibl>. With <cit><quote>on:</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.3.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 3, 77</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>